message.description: This is the error message returned during the window.onerror handler

stack.description: This is the stack trace of the error returned during the window.onerror handler, this is not available in all browsers and may only show up in certain ones (IEs)

line.description: This is the js line the unhandled exception happened on

col.description: This is the js column the unhandled exception happened on

url.description: This url of the js file that errored

unMinStack.description: This is the un minified stack trace of the error returned during the window.onerror handler
